{"tid":1050681,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"化妝師岀路一問","createTime":"2019-03-07T04:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T12:02:36.000Z","uid":219698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"50df5bac859a2fdc6148c4ea1d91e9c3373c5221","tid":1050681,"uid":219698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"唔係好識諗標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n背景：20歲絲<br />\n大半年前讀咗個專業化妝師證書<br />\n因為貪玩 所以做緊飲食業嘅part time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家都要的起心肝搵化妝師full time <br />\n其實係想做新娘化妝師嘅<br />\n但始終新仔一個 咩經驗都冇就幫人化妝好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以打算搵化妝專櫃嘅full Time做住先<br />\n其實本身諗住跟師傅 但因為屋企嘅關係一定要有收入 至少養到自己先 所以放棄左呢個念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問有冇絲打做呢行 想取下經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04fda2973b398f1c2f09b83c2a56b6fda2755282","tid":1050681,"uid":219698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:53:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60737f696cc061e17e3a9ea829f775d1dfeed79","tid":1050681,"uid":219698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:57:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e8a584aab81917a67c863e8f95b650d002349c","tid":1050681,"uid":219698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"推到有人應為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2abd858f24d5821d68e96a02c1920bd2393b9ab","tid":1050681,"uid":219698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8667bffd30de8f6299d8d7c31cd0ac98a66cd313","tid":105068